109
00:05:33.067 --> 00:05:34.401
Yeah...

110
00:05:35.435 --> 00:05:38.206
(CROWD EXCLAIMING. CHEERING)
Nice shot. Alex!

111
00:05:38.306 --> 00:05:42.510
(PLAYERS CHEERING)

112
