That's why I'm glad
you reached out.

113
00:05:44.612 --> 00:05:46.948
I'm just surprised
you have this much time off.

114
00:05:48.348 --> 00:05:51.552
Actually... I retired.

115
00:05:53.321 --> 00:05:55.890
What? (SCOFFS)
(PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING)

116
00:05:55.957 --> 00:05:58.358
I thought
you were gonna do 30 years.

117
