of you two before you go.

141
00:07:12.465 --> 00:07:13.668
ALEX: I got it.

142
00:07:16.203 --> 00:07:18.406
Alex. let's just get
a... a shot.

143
00:07:18.739 --> 00:07:20.508
Mom.
No. come on. It'll be quick.

144
00:07:20.574 --> 00:07:21.676
Just get closer.

145
00:07:22.710 --> 00:07:26.080
Oh. come on. closer than that.
(CHUCKLES) Come on. Smile!

146
00:07:26.147 --> 00:07:26.948
(CHUCKLES)

147
00:07:27.014 --> 00:07:28.783
(CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING)
(CHUCKLES)

148
00:07:28.849 --> 00:07:30.985
Not bad. Okay. Uh...
Yeah.

149
00:07:31.652 --> 00:07:32.954
Just call me every day.
Yes.

150
00:07:33.020 --> 00:07:35.122
JANINE: I love you.
I love you too. Bye.

151
00:07:38.092 --> 00:07:40.027
Okay. Please make sure
she calls every day.

152
00:07:40.094 --> 00:07:42.063
I will pick up.
even if I'm on shift.

153
00:07:42.129 --> 00:07:42.897
Of course.

154
00:07:43.030 --> 00:07:45.498
She may not act like it now.
but one day...

155
00:07:45.599 --> 00:07:47.068
she will appreciate this.

156
00:07:50.972 --> 00:07:53.607
Better get moving.
JANINE: Yeah. Okay. Um...

157
00:07:53.741 --> 00:07:56.644
Have a good time. you two.
Be safe. Danny.

158
00:07:58.279 --> 00:08:00.247
Take care of her.
I will.

159
00:08:00.314 --> 00:08:01.882
("TONIGHT" PLAYING)

160
00:08:02.249 --> 00:08:04.885
Okay. Bye. Love you.
Bye. Love you.

161
00:08:06.486 --> 00:08:08.022
So. we're doing this.

162
00:08:08.389 --> 00:08:12.093
It's exciting.
Yeah. Totally.

163
00:08:18.899 --> 00:08:22.136
<i>♪ You didn't have to tell me ♪</i>

164
00:08:23.104 --> 00:08:25.673
<i>♪ I already knew ♪</i>

165
00:08:26.540 --> 00:08:30.611
<i>♪ That I had my life backwards ♪</i>

166
00:08:30.678 --> 00:08:32.480
<i>♪ An illusion to choose ♪</i>

167
00:08:32.546 --> 00:08:33.647
(LAUGHS)

168
00:08:34.882 --> 00:08:40.154
<i>♪ I'm trading in my brass ring</i>
<i>Maybe now I'll find some luck ♪</i>

169
00:08:42.089 --> 00:08:46.260
<i>♪ A moment on my hands</i>
<i>Forever prayer ♪</i>

170
00:08:46.327 --> 00:08:48.662
<i>♪ Forever lost ♪</i>

171
00:08:50.531 --> 00:08:52.266
<i>♪ Such a shame ♪</i>

172
00:08:53.634 --> 00:08:56.170
<i>♪ What a thing to choose ♪</i>

173
00:08:57.705 --> 00:09:00.775
<i>♪ I'm out on the gallows ♪</i>

174
00:09:01.575 --> 00:09:07.748
<i>♪ But you're gonna save me ♪</i>

175
00:09:09.050 --> 00:09:12.720
(SONG CONCLUDES)
(CAR ENGINE STOPS)

176
00:09:16.757 --> 00:09:19.160
(INDISTINCT CHATTER
