177
00:09:19.226 --> 00:09:20.861
Yo.
ALEX: Huh?

178
00:09:21.729 --> 00:09:22.696
Wanna use the bathroom?

179
00:09:22.797 --> 00:09:25.666
Oh. no. I'm good.
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

180
00:09:25.733 --> 00:09:28.969
