(BOTH GASP)

771
00:42:20.041 --> 00:42:22.176
ALEX: Dad!
(CYRUS SCREAMS. GROANS)

772
00:42:22.276 --> 00:42:24.845
Alex. run!
(ALEX PANTS. GRUNTS)

773
00:42:25.880 --> 00:42:28.682
(DANIEL GRUNTS)
(CYRUS GROANS)

774
00:42:30.718 --> 00:42:32.486
