775
00:42:32.920 --> 00:42:34.288
Where do you think you're going?

776
00:42:34.355 --> 00:42:36.157
(GRUNTS. PANTS)

777
00:42:36.223 --> 00:42:37.291
(DANIEL PANTS)

778
00:42:37.425 --> 00:42:39.226
ALEX: No!
Alex. run! (GRUNTS)

779
00:42:39.360 --> 00:42:41.262
(SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY. GRUNTS)
(GRUNTS) Let me go!

780
00:42:41.328 --> 00:42:42.563
(GROANS)
(PROWLERS GRUNT)

781
00:42:42.696 --> 00:42:44.632
ANGUS: Come here!
(GROANS)

782
00:42:44.765 --> 00:42:47.134
(ALEX SCREAMS)
Damn it. just frickin'...

783
00:42:47.568 --> 00:42:49.937
(GRUNTS)
(GROANS)

784
00:42:50.004 --> 00:42:52.406
(BOTH GRUNT)
Stop squirming! God!

785
00:42:52.507 --> 00:42:54.509
(BOTH GRUNT)

786
00:42:54.575 --> 00:42:55.544
(NICKY GROANS)

787
00:42:56.077 --> 00:42:59.847
(CHOKES) Stop fucking moving!
(GRUNTS)
ALEX: (GRUNTS) Dad!

788
00:43:00.515 --> 00:43:01.550
(DANIEL GRUNTS)
(ANGUS GROANS)

789
00:43:01.715 --> 00:43:04.051
(GRUNTS)
(SCREAMS. GRUNTS)

790
00:43:04.985 --> 00:43:06.921
(ALEX GRUNTS)
(GASPS. CHOKES)

791
00:43:06.987 --> 00:43:09.657
GAR: No! (SCREAMS)
(DANIEL GROANS)

792
00:43:10.224 --> 00:43:11.225
No!

793
00:43:11.358 --> 00:43:13.928
(DANIEL GROANS)
(GRUNTS)

794
00:43:15.196 --> 00:43:17.731
(GAR GRUNTS)
(GRUNTS)

795
00:43:17.832 --> 00:43:20.734
(GROANS. PANTS)
(GRUNTS)

796
00:43:20.835 --> 00:43:23.737
I'm gonna rip
your fucking heart out! (GRUNTS)

797
00:43:23.838 --> 00:43:26.974
(PANTS) Dad! No!
(GAR GRUNTS)

798
00:43:27.675 --> 00:43:29.944
(ALEX GRUNTS)

799
00:43:30.111 --> 00:43:32.213
(DANIEL GRUNTS)

800
00:43:32.346 --> 00:43:35.182
(GRUNTS)
(GROANS)

801
00:43:35.282 --> 00:43:36.484
ALEX: Dad! No!

802
00:43:36.551 --> 00:43:39.220
