by the north fork.

922
00:52:02.523 --> 00:52:04.525
And for the love of God.
shut the fuck up.

923
00:52:04.759 --> 00:52:08.295
I can hear you over a mile away.
Come on. come on. come on.

924
00:52:08.362 --> 00:52:11.365
Follow me.
I told you to shut the fuck up!

925
00:52:12.199 --> 00:52:14.267
Yeah. just keep your mouth shut.

926
00:52:23.645 --> 00:52:26.246
Ah!
(GRUNTS)

927
00:52:27.147 --> 00:52:32.386
(BOTH GRUNT)

928
00:52:34.722 --> 00:52:37.659
(BOTH GRUNT)

929
00:52:38.860 --> 00:52:40.628
(CYRUS WHISPERS) Take a break.

930
00:52:40.695 --> 00:52:42.630
(SHUSHES)

931
00:52:43.097 --> 00:52:46.868
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

932
00:52:46.968 --> 00:52:49.269
(YELPS)

933
00:52:55.777 --> 00:52:57.078
Dad. I found her.

934
00:52:57.177 --> 00:52:58.880
(BOTH GRUNT)

935
00:53:00.414 --> 00:53:01.783
Fuck it. Go. Come on.

936
00:53:01.883 --> 00:53:03.216
(GASPS)

937
00:53:03.751 --> 00:53:05.019
She's this way!

938
00:53:05.153 --> 00:53:10.357
(BOTH GRUNT)

939
00:53:12.225 --> 00:53:13.695
(YELPS)

940
00:53:13.861 --> 00:53:15.462
(BOTH GRUNT)

941
00:53:17.799 --> 00:53:21.102
ALEX: Dad. run! They're coming!
Go! Across the river.

942
00:53:21.334 --> 00:53:24.005
Oh. my god!
Go! We got him!

943
00:53:24.337 --> 00:53:26.674
Let's go. Let's go. Push!

944
00:53:27.240 --> 00:53:28.509
Go. go!

945
00:53:28.676 --> 00:53:29.911
