951
00:53:55.103 --> 00:53:56.336
Oh.

952
00:53:58.371 --> 00:53:59.874
We need to jump.

953
00:54:00.041 --> 00:54:01.209
ALEX: No. no. no. no.

954
00:54:01.341 --> 00:54:03.711
Yes. You have to trust me.
It looks deep enough.

955
00:54:03.845 --> 00:54:05.780
Go. Boys. this way!

956
00:54:06.013 --> 00:54:07.347
