No! No! No!

975
00:55:27.995 --> 00:55:32.867
No! Dad! Dad! Dad! Dad!

976
00:55:33.301 --> 00:55:36.771
Dad! No!

977
00:55:37.238 --> 00:55:41.542
No! Dad! Dad!

978
00:55:43.443 --> 00:55:47.782
